            Request Items
          

Request Items from other libraries.










            Print (Rockford Campus)
          

Printing is available to UIC students, faculty, residents, staff and visitors.










            Access Library Resources From Off-Campus
          

Current UIC affiliates (students, faculty and staff) can access University Library resources from remote computers.










            Search for Articles in Databases and Journals
          

You can search for articles in databases and journals.










            Get Help With Writing, Style and Citations
          

The UIC Library has resources to help you with writing, style and citations.










            Make an Online Appointment with a Librarian
          

Schedule a One-on-One Online Research Consultation with a Librarian.










